text: Clark County is a county in the U.S. state of Idaho. As of the 2020 census, 790 people lived there. The county seat and largest city is Dubois. == Communities == === Cities === * Dubois (county seat) * Spencer === Unincorporated communities === * Humphrey * Kilgore == References == Category:1919 establishments in Idaho Category:Idaho counties
